<div class="content-section">
  <h2>Mouse Polling Rate Guide</h2>
  <p>Polling rate is how often your mouse reports its position to the computer per second. Higher polling rate means smoother and more responsive cursor movement — essential for competitive gaming.</p>
  <table class="rate-table">
    <thead><tr><th>Polling Rate</th><th>Interval</th><th>Best For</th><th>Rating</th></tr></thead>
